{"title":"Install certain python version in Linux","uid":"83fc4bf0106b2e566bb88fa07ace1ff9","slug":"Deploy/Linux/install certain python version in Linux","date":"2023-10-25T17:22:23.000Z","updated":"2023-10-27T18:39:57.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Deploy/Linux/install certain python version in Linux.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JBR-Bunjie/JBR-Bunjie/main/back.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"install-certain-python-version-in-linux\">Install certain python\r\nversion in Linux</h1>\r\n<h2 id=\"for-ubuntu\">-1: for Ubuntu:</h2>\r\n<p>just: apt install python3.8</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"zero-try-to-download-python3.8-through-yum\">Zero, try to\r\ndownload python3.8 through yum</h2>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">yum list | grep python3</code></pre>\r\n<p>find no python38, so choose to setup python3.8 through make\r\ninstall</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"first-download-the-python-file\">First, download the python\r\nfile</h2>\r\n<p>go to website: https://www.python.org/ftp/python to choose correct\r\nfile</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>example:\r\nhttps://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.8.10/Python-3.8.10.tgz</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wget https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.python.org&#x2F;ftp&#x2F;python&#x2F;3.8.10&#x2F;Python-3.8.10.tgz</code></pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"unzip-make-and-install\">unzip, make and install</h2>\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li>在编译前先在/usr/local 建一个文件夹 python3（作为 python\r\n的安装路径，以免覆盖老的版本）</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3</code></pre>\r\n<ol start=\"2\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>解压：</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">tar -zxvf Python-3.8.10.tgz</code></pre>\r\n<ol start=\"3\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>进行指定目录的编译安装</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">.&#x2F;configure --prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3 # 设置编译安装路径\n\nmake # 编译\n\nmake install # 安装</code></pre>\r\n<ol start=\"4\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>创建软链接</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3  &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3.8\n\n# 修改旧版本软连接：ln -s &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3  &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;pythonv</code></pre>\r\n<h2 id=\"检验安装\">检验安装</h2>\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">python3.8 -V\n# Python 3.8.10</code></pre>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/leon-zyl/p/8422699.html\">centOS\r\n下升级 python 版本，详细步骤 - leon-zyl - 博客园 (cnblogs.com)</a></p>\r\n","text":"Install certain python version in Linux -1: for Ubuntu: just: apt install python3.8 Zero, try to download python3.8 through yum yum list | g...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":10,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#install-certain-python-version-in-linux\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Install certain python\r\nversion in Linux</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#for-ubuntu\"><span class=\"toc-text\">-1: for Ubuntu:</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zero-try-to-download-python3.8-through-yum\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Zero, try to\r\ndownload python3.8 through yum</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=